《飢餓遊戲：自由幻夢》被改編成[[電影|電影]]，將分成上下兩集於2014年與2015年上映<ref>{{cite web|first=David|last=Robert|url=http://movienight.mtv.ca/2011/11/woody-harrelson-talks-hunger-games/|title=Woody Harrelson Talks 'Hunger Games'|publisher=MTV|date=November 18, 2011|accessdate=May 21, 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120529022508/http://movienight.mtv.ca/2011/11/woody-harrelson-talks-hunger-games/|archivedate=2012-05-29}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2012/07/10/mockingjay-split-release-dates/|title='Mockingjay' to be split into two movies, release dates announced|publisher=EW.com|date=July 10, 2012|accessdate=October 27, 2012|archive-date=2015-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150111082403/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2012/07/10/mockingjay-split-release-dates/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由[[珍妮佛·勞倫斯|珍妮佛·勞倫斯]]、[[喬許·哈卻森|喬許·哈卻森]]和[[連恩·漢斯沃|連恩·漢斯沃]]飾演凱妮絲、比德與蓋爾。

